node.text: Tiffany Blue® isn’t the only blue we care about. Since its inception in 2000, The Tiffany & Co. Foundation has awarded over $26 million to organizations that support coral and marine conservation in more than 30 countries around the world. In the face of climate change, it is imperative we act now to protect this source of life, food, beauty and recreation. It’s about time we started to make waves. Link in bio for more. #WorldOceansDay #TiffanySustainability

Chef @mvoltaggio and designer and stylist @samimiro take over T Time, our Instagram Live series. Add the below ingredients to your shopping list and follow along with the couple as they put a Tiffany twist on holiday hors d’oeuvres. #TiffanyAndCo  
 
Ingredients: 
4 oz smoked salmon 
¼ cup cream cheese (whipped)
1 bunch of chives (for gold strings)
1 tablespoon of chives (for mix) 
Zest of ½ lemon 
5 eggs 
3 cups milk 
1 cup flour 
1 tablespoon butterfly pea flower powder 
¼ tablespoon caviar (per pouch)
Edible gold luster powder
Salt and black pepper (to taste)

node.text: Style expert @chrisellelim takes over T Time, our Instagram Live series that takes place every Thursday at 3:30 PM EDT. See how she layers jewelry with the new Tiffany T1 collection and find out the secret behind her famous iced coffee.  #TiffanyT1 #TiffanyT #TTime

node.text: For over 180 years (and counting), we’ve handcrafted our timepieces in Switzerland. The new watches from the Tiffany 1837 Makers collection honor that legacy and continue the tradition. Link in bio to shop. #Tiffany1837Makers #MakeItTiffany #TiffanyAndCo

node.text: Tiffany 1837 Makers watches are for the doers, the creators and the changers—those who know time doesn’t bind us, it’s what makes us who we are. Link in bio to shop. #Tiffany1837Makers #MakeItTiffany #TiffanyAndCo

Beautiful @anyataylorjoy at the #Emmys wearing Elsa Peretti® Diamonds by the Yard® necklaces of over 30 total carats and diamond earrings of over 10 total carats.
